OL,6,FA Moroccan asylum seeker who said he
OL,7,Fwas inspired by "revenge" for the
OL,8,FIsrael-Hamas conflict has been
OL,9,Fsentenced to life in prison, with a
OL,10,Fminimum term of 45 years, for
OL,11,Fmurdering a pensioner in the street.
OL,13,FAhmed Alid, 45, stabbed Terence
OL,14,FCarney, 70, six times in Hartlepool
OL,15,Ftown centre early on 15 October last
OL,16,Fyear ` eight days after Hamas attacked
OL,17,FIsrael.
