OL,6,FAt around 5am, minutes earlier, the 45-
OL,7,Fyear-old broke into the locked bedroom
OL,8,Fof his housemate Javed Nouri and
OL,9,Fhacked at him while he slept.
OL,11,FLast month Alid was of the murder of
OL,12,FMr Carney, the attempted murder of Mr
OL,13,FNouri, and assaulting two detectives.
OL,15,FOn Friday 17 May, Alid was sentenced
OL,16,Fat Teesside Crown Court to 19 years,
OL,17,F52 days for the attempted murder of
OL,18,FJaved Nouri. This will be served
OL,19,Fconcurrently, for the murder of
OL,20,FTerence Carney, which he will serve 44
OL,21,Fyears and 52 days.
