OL,6,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb declared: "No
OL,7,Fperiod of incarceration will be
OL,8,Fequivalent to the life he has taken."
OL,10,FThe judge said Alid "attacked and
OL,11,Fmurdered Terrence Carney in a
OL,12,Fterrorist attack" and told him: "You
OL,13,Fintended to intimidate and influence
OL,14,Fthe British government" on their
OL,15,Finternational policy regarding Israel
OL,16,Fand Palestine.
OL,18,FMrs Justice Cheema-Grubb told Alid at
OL,19,Fhis sentencing that he wanted to
OL,20,F"frighten the people of Britain", and
OL,21,Fordered that he be taken down.
