OL,7,FDunkerley is Head of Counter Terrorism
OL,8,FPolicing North East who led the
OL,9,Finvestigation, supported by Cleveland
OL,10,FPolice.
OL,12,FHe said: "In this case, it was
OL,13,Fappropriate that the decision to
OL,14,Fdeclare this horrific incident as an
OL,15,Fact of terrorism was made once all the
OL,16,Fevidence had been heard by the court.
