OL,6,F"Nothing can justify the actions of
OL,7,Fthe defendant that day. I have no
OL,8,Fdoubt that the bravery of the
OL,9,FCleveland officers involved in the
OL,10,Finitial response prevented further
OL,11,Fharm or loss of life that morning.
OL,12,FToday's sentence reflects the shocking
OL,13,Fand horrendous nature of the crimes
OL,14,Fthis man has committed.
